'''Ta-Bitjet''' is an ancient goddess of [[Egyptian mythology]].  She is identified as the consort of [[Horus the Elder|Haroeris]].  Ta-Bitjet is a [[scorpion goddess (disambiguation)|scorpion goddess]] and the blood that flowed from when Horus/Haroeris ruptured her [[hymen]] can serve as a [[panacea (medicine)|panacea]] for all poisons. She could be associated with another bride of one of the [[Horus|Horuses]], [[Serket]].

